Notice.title: Independence Day Celebration
Notice.content:
This is to inform you that our school will celebrate Independence Day on August 16, 2025 in the school premises. The program will commence at 8:00 AM with the flag-hoisting ceremony, followed by cultural performances.

All students and staff are requested to attend in proper school uniform.
